{"image_id": "MPC_2015_page_60", "image_size": [1257, 1632], "ocr": [{"text": "The demand for gasoline is seasonal, with the highest demand usually occurring during the summer driving", "bbox": [153.2, 149.8, 1103.7, 170.6]}, {"text": "season. Margins from the sale of merchandise tend to be less volatile than margins from the retail sale of gasoline", "bbox": [153.2, 174.8, 1103.6, 195.7]}, {"text": "and diesel fuel. Merchandise margin as a percent of total gross margin for Speedway decreased in 2015,", "bbox": [153.2, 199.8, 1103.8, 220.7]}, {"text": "primarily due to higher light product margins during the year and the effects of the convenience stores acquired", "bbox": [153.2, 224.8, 1103.6, 245.7]}, {"text": "from Hess. The following table sets forth Speedway merchandise statistics for the past three years.", "bbox": [153.2, 249.8, 976.8, 270.7]}, {"text": "Speedway Merchandise Statistics", "bbox": [153.2, 295.2, 404.4, 314.0]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [854.4, 295.2, 891.9, 314.0]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [946.6, 295.2, 984.1, 314.0]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1046.7, 295.2, 1084.2, 314.0]}, {"text": "Merchandise sales (in millions)", "bbox": [153.2, 334.8, 389.3, 353.6]}, {"text": "$ 4,879", "bbox": [842.7, 334.8, 903.7, 353.6]}, {"text": "$ 3,611", "bbox": [934.9, 334.8, 995.9, 353.6]}, {"text": "$ 3,135", "bbox": [1027.2, 334.8, 1088.1, 353.6]}, {"text": "Merchandise gross margin (in millions)", "bbox": [153.2, 366.1, 450.3, 384.8]}, {"text": "1,368", "bbox": [861.4, 366.1, 903.7, 384.8]}, {"text": "975", "bbox": [967.8, 366.1, 995.9, 384.8]}, {"text": "825", "bbox": [1060.0, 366.1, 1088.1, 384.8]}, {"text": "Merchandise as a percent of total gross margin", "bbox": [153.2, 397.3, 503.9, 416.1]}, {"text": "54%", "bbox": [884.9, 397.3, 919.3, 416.1]}, {"text": "57%", "bbox": [977.1, 397.3, 1011.5, 416.1]}, {"text": "65%", "bbox": [1069.4, 397.3, 1103.8, 416.1]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2015, Speedway had 2,766 convenience stores in 22 states. The foll